\":{\"hour\":14,\"minute\":0}},{\"start\":{\"hour\":17,\"minute\":30},\"end\":{\"hour\":23,\"minute\":0}},{\"start\":{\"hour\":11,\"minute\":30},\"end\":{\"hour\":14,\"minute\":0}},{\"start\":{\"hour\":17,\"minute\":30},\"end\":{\"hour\":23,\"minute\":0}},{\"start\":{\"hour\":11,\"minute\":30},\"end\":{\"hour\":14,\"minute\":0}},{\"start\":{\"hour\":17,\"minute\":30},\"end\":{\"hour\":23,\"minute\":30}},{\"start\":{\"hour\":11,\"minute\":30},\"end\":{\"hour\":14,\"minute\":0}},{\"start\":{\"hour\":17,\"minute\":30},\"end\":{\"hour\":23,\"minute\":30}},{\"start\":{\"hour\":11,\"minute\":30},\"end\":{\"hour\":14,\"minute\":30}},{\"start\":{\"hour\":17,\"minute\":0},\"end\":{\"hour\":23,\"minute\":30}}],\"rating\":4.1,\"reviews\":[{\"author_name\":\"rovan yu\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/112527869459428883223/reviews\",\"language\":\"zh-Hant\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKUkeGNo6bPZh3RFcC8srO9g9f1cwKKw0u4oBs1e6_6sJ3n0g=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5\",\"rating\":4,\"relative_time_description\":\"1 個月前\",\"text\":\"服務人員還蠻勤換烤網，但最後要上甜點的時候反而沒有把桌子收乾淨，有點可惜功虧一簣啊～我們兩大兩小點了一個兩人套餐，再加單點其他的～當月壽星加入會員會送牛五花跟泡菜一份也不錯～\\n\\n覺得令人驚艷的有雞橫隔膜，整個烤熟之後很香超有嚼勁很好吃～另外日式麻糬，很慢很慢烤到麻糬膨脹起來超可愛的，沾一點黑糖跟黃豆粉，來不及拍照就吃掉了，超級意猶未盡😋沙拉跟白飯跟泡菜算中規中矩可以墊墊胃～還有加點的培根蘆筍卷非常不錯，培根的基本油脂可以襯托出蘆筍的脆甜，注意火候烤熟豬肉趁熱吃非常好吃，推薦加點！綜合海鮮有柳葉魚、干貝跟蝦子；干貝加一點雞湯烤到雞湯滾了基本上就可以吃，新鮮多汁！柳葉魚有蛋喔，要有耐心慢慢烤熟不要焦了～\\n\\n加點的牛舌最基本款不推，太薄了沒有很好吃，不過是最基本款190元自己選的自己負責，哈，之前去新橋竹北店吃的最高等級厚切牛舌一份450元，超讚👍\",\"time\":1744508103,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"Bryce Chen\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110449116833850033989/reviews\",\"language\":\"zh-Hant\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJUc_6mu2X1XOhgw6lhQ7r9VY-WjH_RExsSnKI8I3pxFur6FBo=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4\",\"rating\":5,\"relative_time_description\":\"2 週前\",\"text\":\"新竹才有的在地燒肉店，過往在竹北店的用餐體驗不錯，所以這次選擇來新竹市區的府後店用餐。\\n\\n燒肉價格合理，店家亦有提供幾款價格划算的套餐供選擇，燒肉的肉質都算是新鮮，桌邊有提供雞湯，餐後也有招待紫米粥作為甜點。\\n\\n推薦大家到新竹可以來用餐～\",\"time\":1747743156,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"鄭壯志\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/117818583020305490055/reviews\",\"language\":\"zh-Hant\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUZbXb9x-vaGdV29T8usc0VZ1qtrV7Xt1_CALLmbyrqHpXKoVvs=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5\",\"rating\":5,\"relative_time_description\":\"4 週前\",\"text\":\"CP值很高的燒肉店👍\\n推薦雪花牛、松阪豬、透抽、厚切牛舌🎉\\n甜點是紫米紅豆粥加一分🥣\\n吃到滿滿的幸福感🎊\",\"time\":1746779467,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"陳小萱\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102920450829076656169/reviews\",\"language\":\"zh-Hant\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW__tAiAMrz73wq_upbbOfMOrpKFjCLcAIqMMeDb-FgcZE0rco=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5\",\"rating\":4,\"relative_time_description\":\"3 個月前\",\"text\":\"服務生很勤勞換烤網，餐點品質中規中矩，高湯很清淡，線上點餐操作容易，套餐份量也很足夠。使用炭火燒烤，偶爾會回來吃個氛圍感。少一顆星是因為沒有壽星生日優惠⋯\",\"time\":1741355337,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"sam liu\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109898001552008622299/reviews\",\"language\":\"zh-Hant\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXxaqKefuaDCeDY7VEqx0mB_J4J49MTBsHSZZ1bt_Oyd2dgLuU=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6\",\"rating\":1,\"relative_time_description\":\"4 個月前\",\"text\":\"我們來吃晚餐！\\n可是再來的機會幾乎是渺茫。\\n我叫了四次生菜要包燒肉\\n只來了一次\\n感覺他們就只是送肉，然後再來就是趕緊收盤子\\n中間段隔了一個很大的空間\\n需要人提醒他才檢查我們的單子\\n才又開始送餐品\\n新橋燒肉在新竹名氣很大\\n有一點點感覺他們的肉現在品質沒那麼好\\n以前是吃過新竹的，另一間分店、\\n也吃過竹北店\\n以前吃的都不會覺得如此的差\\n可是這次讓我感覺的如此的不好\\n，燒肉店這麼多，不去了\",\"time\":1738243304,\"translated\":false}],\"photos\":[\"AXQCQNQdGq_KfWRSCGd3xyCxwklc1xyxxz5QAnDpEvc-iTSKU63wEgJwC0DGzqvYtzgJ1zBqtLvMsLSXMW3OmyGLiw9UJE5K-tO-GcFGB56VObkBEPPrKJf5oLjLMtR7lZE-a5YFAGSaPx7mOJpoivcCWWC59Kp-KLLOabalOfUW-buQrXFbVv4cLIQBKyrR2O28PFabPatdSRKCbflwW4RecLOci2F7KmuhDx-jG8j506PVBE-rJmfMhJI__G7v_I0cs5PYewvgWuu_lJImEbgIGQ7zkHtbrw3gNPMFMJHuNLsBeJDxud9OHG4bWAA1aeQ5nDxgT4_85Ho\",\"AXQCQNSs4SXLE5QmhqVG36xryFinS6iGA2UZ_UHpwkiX0csAUhNXwJq5It84czSi